?','[\"app.listen()\", \"app.start()\", \"app.run()\", \"http.startServer()\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73e4854d-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Briefly describe req and res in Express.','[\"req is the incoming request object (headers, body, params); res is the response object used to send data back to the client (res.send, res.json, res.status).\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73e5283a-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','How do you define a route that accepts a numeric id parameter?','[\"app.get(\'/items/:id\', handler)\", \"app.get(\'/items/id\', handler)\", \"app.get(\'/items/?id\', handler)\", \"app.get(\'/items/(id)\', handler)\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73e58002-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','Query parameters are accessed via req.params in Express.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',1,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73e6e2a4-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','What happens if a middleware neither calls next() nor sends a response?','[\"The request hangs and the client times out\", \"Express calls next() automatically\", \"An error is thrown immediately\", \"The response is sent with status 204\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73e72ec8-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Give an example use-case for middleware in Express.','[\"Examples include logging, authentication checks, parsing request bodies, input validation, and error handling middleware.\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73e8033c-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','What is the signature of an Express error-handling middleware?','[\"(err, req, res, next)\", \"(req, res, next, err)\", \"(req, res)\", \"(err, next)\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73e84f61-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','An error-handling middleware must be added after other middleware and routes to catch their errors.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73e96d53-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which middleware parses incoming JSON payloads?','[\"express.json()\", \"express.body()\", \"bodyParser.text()\", \"express.urlencoded()\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ea56cf-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','You should enable body parsing middleware before defining routes that need access to req.body.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73eb005a-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which Mongoose method saves a document instance to the database?','[\"doc.save()\", \"Model.insert()\", \"Model.createInstance()\", \"db.put()\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73eb57fb-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Name a reason to use Mongoose schemas rather than raw MongoDB driver.','[\"Schemas provide structure, validation, middleware (hooks), and convenient model APIs which simplify development and reduce runtime errors.\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ec04c7-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which HTTP method is typically used to update an existing resource partially?','[\"PATCH\", \"GET\", \"POST\", \"DELETE\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ec4e1a-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','List the typical endpoints for a resource \'users\' in a CRUD API.','[\"GET /users, GET /users/:id, POST /users, PUT or PATCH /users/:id, DELETE /users/:id\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ece816-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which library is commonly used with Express for validation middleware?','[\"express-validator\", \"react-validate\", \"lodash.validate\", \"body-guard\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ed3292-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','Validation should always happen before writing to the database.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ede01a-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which pagination method is more performant for large datasets?','[\"cursor-based pagination\", \"offset-based pagination\", \"full-scan pagination\", \"page-number only pagination\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ee3627-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Name one drawback of offset-based pagination.','[\"Offset pagination can be slow for large offsets and may return inconsistent results if the underlying dataset changes between requests.\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ef5d76-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which token type is commonly stored in localStorage for SPA auth (though with security caveats)?','[\"JWT\", \"Session ID cookie\", \"Opaque database key\", \"CSRF token\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73efb3d2-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Give one security risk of storing JWT in localStorage.','[\"LocalStorage is vulnerable to XSS; malicious scripts can read tokens and exfiltrate them.\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f06ca1-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which library is commonly used in Node to sign and verify JWTs?','[\"jsonwebtoken\", \"jwt-node\", \"express-jwt\", \"body-jwt\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f0b460-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','A JWT must be encrypted to be secure.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',1,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f14d7f-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which package helps set secure HTTP headers in Express?','[\"helmet\", \"cors\", \"morgan\", \"express-rate-limit\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f19790-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','CORS configuration is only needed for browsers and not for server-to-server requests.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f2993c-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which tool is commonly used for end-to-end HTTP testing of Express apps?','[\"supertest\", \"mocha-http\", \"http-tester\", \"express-test\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f2deee-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Why are integration tests with a running server useful for APIs?','[\"They test the actual HTTP layer, middleware integration, routing and serialization, catching issues that unit tests of handlers may miss.\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f36858-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which package is commonly used for request logging in Express?','[\"morgan\", \"winston-express\", \"log4js-express\", \"express-logger\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f3af27-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','Rate limiting should be applied globally and sometimes per-route for sensitive endpoints.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f48e96-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','What is the 12-factor recommendation for storing config?','[\"In environment variables\", \"In source code\", \"In a local JSON file tracked in git\", \"In user input at runtime\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f4d791-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','How should secrets be provided to a containerized app in production?','[\"Use orchestration secrets (Kubernetes Secrets), environment variables injected by CI/CD, or secret managers (AWS Secrets Manager, HashiCorp Vault), not checked-in files.\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f57455-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which logger is known for being very fast and JSON-friendly?','[\"pino\", \"console.log\", \"morgan\", \"winston (legacy)\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f5bcde-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','Structured logs (JSON) are easier to query and parse in log aggregators than plain text logs.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f67478-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which of the following is NOT typically part of an API production checklist?','[\"Unrestricted debug logs enabled\", \"Health checks configured\", \"Proper error reporting\", \"Rate limiting for public endpoints\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f6cede-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Name two items you should test before deploying an API.','[\"Examples: behavior under load (performance), authentication flows, critical route responses, error handling, and security checks such as CORS and input validation.\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f786e8-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which status code is appropriate for validation errors?','[\"400\", \"200\", \"500\", \"401\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f7d567-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e