quests, validate input, handle files, and implement middleware patterns for cross-cutting concerns.',2,'2026-05-15 17:03:11','2026-05-15 17:03:11'),('cee1053e-5066-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','Building RESTful APIs with Databases','Design and implement RESTful endpoints integrated with a database, including patterns for modeling, queries, and transactions.',3,'2026-05-15 17:03:11','2026-05-15 17:03:11'),('cee246fd-5066-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','Security, Authentication, and Testing','Protect APIs, implement authentication and authorization, and verify behavior through automated tests.',4,'2026-05-15 17:03:11','2026-05-15 17:03:11');
